Class PlacedPiece

  • java.lang.Object
    • aeneas.models.PlacedPiece
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class PlacedPiece
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Contains a piece and a location. This represents a piece that has been placed (or is going to be placed) on the board.

      • getSquaresInBoardFrame

        public Square[] getSquaresInBoardFrame()
        Get the list of squares of this piece, offset by the piece location. For instance, if row = 5, col = 6, and pieces contains the square with row=3, col=4, then this will return an array containing a square with row=8, col=10.
        Returns:
        The list of squares
